BY STRIVING TO ANSWER
QUESTIONS LIKE THESE,

00:01:39.000 --> 00:01:41.000
EARTH SCIENTISTS
HELP US UNDERSTAND

00:01:41.000 --> 00:01:42.000
HOW OUR PLANET WORKS.

